com.xilinx.rapidwright.placer.blockplacer

Class BlockPlacer

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.placer.blockplacer.AbstractBlockPlacer<HardMacro,Site>
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.placer.blockplacer.BlockPlacer

  • public class BlockPlacer
extends AbstractBlockPlacer<HardMacro,Site>
    Initial attempt at a pre-implemented module placer. It is more accurate in that it tries to traverse critical paths into both ends of the connections made between hard macros.
